# Website UI freeze

These paths are the **Next.js website**. They are frozen.

- Do **not** edit to add features, polish UI, or “keep parity” with the mobile app.
- Shared API routes live under `app/api/**` — those may change when the **mobile app** needs them; prefer not touching `page.tsx` / site `components/**`.
- Lift only when the user explicitly says the website is in scope again.
